<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Simply give us a call to book your multi-centre holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? Consider it done. Dial in and let our experts plan your dream getaway. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><em>*Prices are based on 2 people sharing for 4 nights in a Twin Room at Hotel Masson, Montreux and 3 nights in a South Facing Twin Room at Hotel Stella, Interlaken with trains transfers between resorts and an upgrade to the golden pass carriage included, departing on the 7th June 25 from London Gatwick airport. Supplements for alternative flights, flight routes, and room types may apply. Prices are correct at the time of publishing on 27/11/24 but are subject to change based on availability. Please call for the most up-to-date pricing and availability before booking.</em></p>]]></description>
