  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p><span>Make the most of your trip to Switzerland and explore Montreux and Interlaken, taking the scenic ‘</span><a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-switzerland/goldenpass-line" title="GoldenPass Line">Golden Pass</a><span>’ train between the two. Wander through the Lavaux vineyards of Lake Geneva, cruise on Lake Thun or Brienz, see the incredible scenery of the Jungfrau region, topped off by a visit to the iconic Jungfraujoch - Top of Europe.</span></p>]]></listingDescription>
  <listingImage><![CDATA[umb://media/a89612371b7c4bf1bc67ab2603a12704]]></listingImage>
